2
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:34,000
cî û welatê Kurda, şêrîn û Kurdistan î.
 
the place and the land of the Kurds, is sweet Kurdistan.

3
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:39,000
Were keko tu zanî, ji derda re derman î,
 
Come brother, you know, you are the cure for the pain,

4
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:44,000
cî û welatê Kurda, şêrîn û Kurdistan î.
 
the place and the land of the Kurds, is sweet Kurdistan.

5
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:48,000
Gur ketiye nav pezê me, xayîn pir e li nav me,
 
A wolf has entered our flock, there are many traitors among
us,

6
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:53,000
hawar ji hesreta ne, tina bînî halê me.
 
alas from longing, you don't see our condition.

7
