Ketin em bi destê te, dil xerap ji qestê te,
 
We fell into your hands, the heart is ruined because of your
intent,

10
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:11,000
ez zanim ji Xwedê ne, tû nizanî em kîne.
 
I know it is from God, you don't know who we are.

11
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:15,000
Ketin em bi destê te, dil xerap ji qestê te,
 
We fell into your hands, the heart is ruined because of your
intent,

12
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:20,000
ez zanim ji Xwedê ne, tû nizanî em kîne.
 
I know it is from God, you don't know who we are.

13
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:25,000
Hunermend im çi bêjim, bi derd û kul dinalim,
 
I am an artist, what can I say, I groan with pain and
sorrow,

14
